									<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>The objective of the Information Technology Office is to guarantee the efficient operation of data communication networks as well as the other general network services within University.</p>
<p>The activities of the Office are:</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square;">
<li>planning and developing the IT infrastructure of the University.</li>
<li>preventing problems and resolving critical situations that occur in the IT infrastructure of the University.</li>
</ul>
<p>If you encounter IT problems, please contact the Information Technology Office.</p>
<p>The Office recommends that you give them advance notice regarding any planned activities that might affect the provision of IT services (e.g. you want to obtain new software or hardware, relocate desks and computers, renovate rooms, etc).</p> 	</div>

	
